data.description:
Welcome to your charming oasis in the heart of Daytona Beach! Nestled on Verona St, this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts an array of features that combine comfort, convenience, and modern upgrades.Enjoy the luxury and efficiency of a tankless hot water heater, ensuring endless comfort for you and your family. Privacy is paramount, thanks to the vinyl fence enclosing the property featuring a 8 foot opening for all your outdoor toys. Plus, there's a 20x10 shed/outbuilding complete with electricity--perfect for storage or a workshop.Safety and peace of mind are key with the full home security system equipped with closed-circuit video surveillance.Step inside to discover a beautifully remodeled and stylish master bath. The entire home has been treated to a fresh coat of paint, inside and out, radiating a welcoming ambiance from the moment you arrive.  The flooring boasts a tasteful combination of durable tile and water-resistant laminate, offering both style and easy maintenance. Step outside onto the expansive concrete patio, where a retractable sunshade awaits, creating an ideal spot for entertaining, relaxing in the Florida sunshine or enjoying the breezes by the outdoor wood firepit.
But that's not all, this home isn't just a haven; it's surrounded by convenience. Close proximity to fantastic amenities such as a newly built Publix Supermarket, Embry Riddle University, Daytona Beach International Airport, Daytona State University, every restaurant imaginable, Daytona International Speedway, both the Tangler Outlets and the Volusia Mall, and just minutes from the pristine white sands of "The World's Most Famous Beach".
Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously maintained home yours. Schedule a viewing today and envision yourself in this inviting space, where comfort, style, and practicality seamlessly converge.
